It was great being here.

00:41:20.330 --> 00:41:21.663 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Learned a lot from you.

00:41:21.663 --> 00:41:24.990 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: Well, and I always
learn a lot from you as well.

00:41:24.990 --> 00:41:26.540 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It's fascinating.

